<!-- ====== WHY VINYL STAIRCASES ====== -->
<section id="why-vinyl">
  <div class="why-header">
    <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span><span class="eyebrow-text">The Smart Choice</span></div>
    <h2 class="section-title">WHY VINYL<br>STAIRCASES?</h2>
    <div class="gold-rule"></div>
    <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--ash);line-height:1.9;">Carpet wears out. Hardwood scratches and fades. Vinyl stair treads deliver the premium look homeowners across Halifax want, without the drawbacks. Here is why more HRM homeowners are making the switch.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-card">
      <span class="why-card-icon">&#9670;</span>
      <div class="why-card-title">BUILT TO LAST</div>
      <p class="why-card-body">Vinyl stair treads are engineered for high-traffic areas. They resist scratches, dents, and daily wear far better than carpet or traditional hardwood. In a Halifax home with kids, pets, or heavy foot traffic, vinyl holds up year after year without showing its age.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <span class="why-card-icon">&#9670;</span>
      <div class="why-card-title">EFFORTLESS MAINTENANCE</div>
      <p class="why-card-body">No more vacuuming carpet stairs or worrying about spills soaking in. Vinyl treads wipe clean in seconds. No special cleaners, no refinishing, no annual upkeep. They stay looking sharp with almost zero effort.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <span class="why-card-icon">&#9670;</span>
      <div class="why-card-title">PREMIUM APPEARANCE</div>
      <p class="why-card-body">Modern vinyl treads replicate the look of real hardwood or stone with stunning accuracy. You get the high-end aesthetic without the high-end price tag or fragility. Guests will not believe it is vinyl until you tell them.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <span class="why-card-icon">&#9670;</span>
      <div class="why-card-title">SAFER THAN CARPET</div>
      <p class="why-card-body">Loose or worn carpet on stairs is a tripping hazard. Vinyl treads provide a firm, consistent surface with defined nosing edges. They offer better grip underfoot and eliminate the risks that come with aging carpet.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <span class="why-card-icon">&#9670;</span>
      <div class="why-card-title">COST-EFFECTIVE UPGRADE</div>
      <p class="why-card-body">Compared to real hardwood stair refinishing or full staircase rebuilds, vinyl tread installation delivers a dramatic visual upgrade at a fraction of the cost. It is one of the highest-impact improvements you can make in your home.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <span class="why-card-icon">&#9670;</span>
      <div class="why-card-title">MOISTURE & PET FRIENDLY</div>
      <p class="why-card-body">Living in Halifax means dealing with wet boots, snow, and salt. Vinyl is fully waterproof and will not warp, stain, or absorb odours. It is the ideal choice for pet owners and families in the Maritime climate.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

